item.title: Flean
item.description: https://www.fijnopvakantie.nl https://www.buitenbergen.nl What started out as one of most successful holiday rental websites in the Netherlands, www.fijnopvakantie.nl, grew out to be a full-service, hosted holiday rental solution, currently serving than 20 holiday rental websites. The platform allows holiday park owners to increase revenue and improve conversion with a customizable, full-fledged solution taking care of bookings, processing availability (connecting to more than 10 different external booking services) and many other functionalities.
